                  </hi>. I am a plumber. I have two partners—the prisoner was in our employ, and was at work as our journeyman, at No. 10, Belgrave-square—I have no doubt this lead is ours—he was working with such lead.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. A person in the trade gave me the lead.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
